## Buy us some doughnuts

Sapphire Community is and always will be open source, even if we don&#39;t get donations. That being said, we know there are amazing people who may still want to donate just to show their appreciation. Thank you very much in advance!

We accept donations through Open Collective, Ko-fi, PayPal, Patreon, and GitHub Sponsorships. You can use the buttons below to donate through your method of choice.

|   Donate With   |                       Address                       |
| :-------------: | :-------------------------------------------------: |
| Open Collective | [Click Here](https://sapphirejs.dev/opencollective) |
|      Ko-fi      |      [Click Here](https://sapphirejs.dev/kofi)      |
|     Patreon     |    [Click Here](https://sapphirejs.dev/patreon)     |
|     PayPal      |     [Click Here](https://sapphirejs.dev/paypal)     |

